\par \pard \widctlpar 
\par This dialog governs how the references are displayed in the main list; how wide the column for author names is, how many author names to display, and whether to also display the title of the reference.
\par 
\par The {\b Select new items} check box controls whether a newly created reference is automatically selected afterwards.
